3. REQUIRED HELPER FUNCTIONS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Implement all three helpers before build():

section_header(title)
  Returns a full-width Table with BRAND_DARK background and white 11pt bold text.
  Padding: top/bottom=6, left/right=8. No grid lines.

callout(text, label="UNLIKE NEWSELA")
  Returns an amber callout box with a colored left accent bar (0.12in wide).
  - label starts with "▌" for UNLIKE, "★" for UNIQUE
  - Label text is 8pt bold BRAND_ACCENT (verify 4.5:1 on AMBER background)
  - Body text is 8.5pt DKGRAY on AMBER
  - Left accent bar background = BRAND_ACCENT for UNIQUE, RED (#C0392B) for UNLIKE
  - Wrap in KeepTogether([Spacer(1,6), callout, Spacer(1,6)])

side_by_side(img1, caption1, img2, caption2, h=2.5*inch)
  Returns a 2-column Table with each column = W/2. Each cell contains an Image
  (width=W/2 - 0.1in, height=h) followed by a caption in caption_style.
  If an image file is missing, show only the caption. No borders.

img_full(filename, caption_text, h=3.5*inch)
  Returns a centered full-width image with caption below in caption_style.

