  KEY STRENGTHS
    • Bullets in bullet_style
    • Each bullet: "<b>Strength name</b> — explanation"
    • Use label_style color inline via <font color="..."> tag for strength names

  KNOWN LIMITATIONS
    • Bullets in bullet_style  
    • Each bullet: "<b>Limitation name</b> — explanation"
    • Always include AI calibration findings from live testing

  FOOTER (last element in story)
    • HRFlowable width=W thickness=0.5 color=MGRAY spaceAfter=6
    • "Competitive Intelligence Report · [Product Name] · [Date] · Prepared by Claude (Competitive Agent)"
      in footer_style

